                <h2>Nutritional Needs for Goats</h2>
                <p>Proper nutrition is vital for goats to thrive and be productive. Their diet should include:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Forage:</strong> High-quality hay, pasture grasses, and browse are essential.</li>
                    <li><strong>Concentrates:</strong> Grains like barley and oats can supplement their diet.</li>
                    <li><strong>Minerals:</strong> Provide a mineral supplement to ensure they get necessary vitamins and minerals.</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Always provide access to fresh, clean water and adjust the diet based on the goatâ€™s age, production stage, and health status.</p>
