                <h2>Ideal Environment for Goats</h2>
                <p>Goats require a suitable environment to stay healthy and productive:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Shelter:</strong> Provide a well-ventilated shelter that protects from extreme weather.</li>
                    <li><strong>Fencing:</strong> Use strong, high fencing to prevent escapes and protect from predators.</li>
                    <li><strong>Space:</strong> Ensure adequate space for grazing and movement to prevent overcrowding.</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Keep their living area clean to reduce the risk of diseases.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

