                <p>Consistent care practices are key to maintaining goat health:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Regular Check-ups:</strong> Schedule veterinary visits for health assessments and vaccinations.</li>
                    <li><strong>Hoof Care:</strong> Regularly trim hooves to prevent hoof diseases.</li>
                    <li><strong>Parasite Control:</strong> Monitor for signs of parasites and implement control measures as needed.</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Keep detailed records of health interventions and treatments for each goat.</p>
            </div>
